T02TD2221E:62a-1: shr'i ao di ya na bi ni gu hya ma h'a gu hya tattho pa de sha /
T02TD2221E:62a-3: dpal aurgyan nas byung ba gsang ba'i gsang ba chen po de kho na nyid kyi man ngag / dpal rdo rje sems dpa' la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD2221E:62a-4: thugs rje chen po la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD2221E:62a-5: lus gnas cha shas bcas par rtog / nges 'byung de nyid cha shas med //
T02TD2221E:62a-6: cha shas can dang cha med pa //
T02TD2221E:62b-0: shes 'di @62b grol ba the tshom med //
T02TD2221E:62b-1: dngos po thams cad mnyam pa nyid //
T02TD2221E:62b-2: myur du 'jug pa dka' ba nyid //
T02TD2221E:62b-3: dpe dang gtan tshigs rnam par spangs //
T02TD2221E:62b-4: rang bzhin gyis ni 'od gsal zhing //
T02TD2221E:62b-5: gnyug ma ru ni gnas pa ste //
T02TD2221E:62b-6: dpyad pa'i yul las 'das pa yin //
T02TD2221E:62b-7: rtsod med zhi ba mtshon cha med //
T02TD2221E:62b-8: nges pa'i chos kyi dbyings la gnas //
T02TD2221E:62b-9: bskul ba med cing 'gyur ba med //
T02TD2221E:62b-10: shin tu stong zhing rdul med pa //
T02TD2221E:62b-11: sgra las 'das shing yon tan spangs //
T02TD2221E:62b-12: dngos po kun gyis rang bzhin gnas //
T02TD2221E:62b-13: gang zhig 'gro la rnam gnas pa //
T02TD2221E:62b-14: de ni sangs rgyas sku ru rtogs //
T02TD2221E:62b-15: dpe med brtag pa med pa ru //
T02TD2221E:62b-16: mkhas pas ma lus bsgom par bya //
T02TD2221E:62b-17: ma brtags par ni gang rtog pa //
T02TD2221E:62b-18: de yis thams cad brtag pa yin //
T02TD2221E:62b-19: rtog pa de dang sdug bsngal 'khor //
T02TD2221E:62b-20: nga yis rgyud du gsal ma byas //
T02TD2221E:62b-21: shes nyen can la de yi chos ;
T02TD2221E:62b-22: / so so ru ni bstan pa yin //
T02TD2221E:62b-23: nyon mongs sgrib pa med pa dang //
T02TD2221E:62b-24: las rnams thams cad rnam par spangs //
T02TD2221E:62b-25: de nyid 'dir ni rab shes na //
T02TD2221E:62b-26: srid pa'i rtog las rnam grol 'gyur //
T02TD2221E:62b-27: dngos rnams rang bzhin dag pa la //
T02TD2221E:62b-28: rang bzhin nyid du rtog byed pa //
T02TD2221E:62b-29: de yis don dam shes min de //
T02TD2221E:62b-30: las kyi zhags pas bcings pa yin //
T02TD2221E:62b-31: kha cig dkyil 'khor las byed yin //
T02TD2221E:62b-32: kha cig 'gying zhing gsang sngags zlos //
T02TD2221E:62b-33: kha cig dag ni gsang sngags 'chang //
T02TD2221E:62b-34: kha cig sbyin sreg mchod sbyin byed //
T02TD2221E:62b-35: kha cig nga rgyal gyis ni gnas //
T02TD2221E:62b-36: kha cig 'dod chags zhe sdang bsten //
T02TD2221E:62b-37: de kun las kyi 'khor bar gnas //
T02TD2221E:62b-38: gang du 'gro ba gnas gyur pa'i //
T02TD2221E:62b-39: gsang chen 'di ni shes gyur na //
T02TD2221E:62b-40: gang la 'ang sdig pa yod min zhing //
T02TD2221E:62b-41: dgag par bya ba ci yang med //
T02TD2221E:62b-42: las rnams thams cad byas kyang ni //
T02TD2221E:62b-43: gos med skur ni rnam par grol //
T02TD2221E:62b-44: las rnams thams cad de la gnas //
T02TD2221E:62b-45: las rnams kun gyi gtso bo yin //
T02TD2221E:62b-46: sku gsung thugs la sogs pa dang //
T02TD2221E:62b-47: dbang po'i yid bcas shin tu gnas //
T02TD2221E:62b-48: rtag tu legs par dpyad pa ste //
T02TD2221E:63a-2: rang bzhin dag pas sku gsum gnas //
T02TD2221E:63a-3: kun rtog yid kyi shes pa min //
T02TD2221E:63a-4: de bas dngos po thams cad ni //
T02TD2221E:63a-5: nyin mtshan bcas te de la gnas //
T02TD2221E:63a-6: mthong sogs de yi rang bzhin nyid //
T02TD2221E:63a-7: thams cad mkhyen pa rol zhing bzhugs //
T02TD2221E:63a-8: shes rab thabs kyi cho ga yis //
T02TD2221E:63a-9: las dang chos ni mnyam nyid du //
T02TD2221E:63a-10: rnal 'byor pa yis sbyar bar bya //
T02TD2221E:63a-11: mnyam dang mi mnyam snyoms sems pa //
T02TD2221E:63a-12: chos dang las ni mnyam nyid du //
T02TD2221E:63a-13: rnal 'byor pa yis sbyar bar bya //
T02TD2221E:63a-14: yon tan ldan dang yon tan med ;
T02TD2221E:63a-15: / rang nyid byed po sdud po gtso //
T02TD2221E:63a-16: gsang chen 'gro ba la gnas pa //
T02TD2221E:63a-17: mngon pa'i nga rgyal can gyis min //
T02TD2221E:63a-18: sems dang sems byung rang bzhin gyis //
T02TD2221E:63a-19: bde ba chen por rang nyid sad //
T02TD2221E:63a-20: 'khor bar med pa'i dngos po gang //
T02TD2221E:63a-21: byang chub sems kyi rang bzhin bsgom //
T02TD2221E:63a-22: gnyi ga'i rang bzhin dbyer med pa //
T02TD2221E:63a-23: sems kyi rang bzhin shes nas ni //
T02TD2221E:63a-24: sems kyi rgyu ba kun spangs te //
T02TD2221E:63a-25: mnyam pa'i ro la gnas par bya //
T02TD2221E:63a-26: gsang ba chen po gnas med pa //
T02TD2221E:63a-27: rnal 'byor pa yi gsang chen sbyor //
T02TD2221E:63a-28: dpal au rgyan nas byung ba /
T02TD2221E:63a-29: gsang ba'i gsang ba chen po de kho na nyid kyi man ngag ces bya ba slob dpon chen po d'a ri ka pas mdzad pa rdzogs so//
